25:32.155 --> 25:33.448
Marie.

25:38.328 --> 25:39.371
Honey.

25:40.455 --> 25:42.707
What can I do for you? What do you need?

25:42.791 --> 25:44.042
Nothing, I'm good.

25:44.960 --> 25:46.044
Sweetie.

25:47.754 --> 25:50.173
What happened to you,
it's a very big deal.

25:50.465 --> 25:53.385
